flowchart TD
    Start([User Request]) --> Orchestrator[ORCHESTRATOR]
    
    Orchestrator --> Parse[1. Parse<br/>Phân tích request]
    
    Parse --> PlanningAgent[2. Planning Agent<br/>Phân tích & tạo plan]
    
    PlanningAgent --> Decision{Task đơn giản?}
    
    %% Simple path - Direct LLM
    Decision -->|Yes| DirectLLM[Direct LLM<br/>Trả lời trực tiếp]
    DirectLLM --> Format
    
    %% Complex path - Multi-agent
    Decision -->|No| Execute[3. Execute Tasks<br/>Thực thi song song/tuần tự]
    
    Execute -->|Task: Research| Research[Research Agent<br/>Web + Documents]
    Execute -->|Task: Code| Code[Code Agent<br/>Python execution]
    Execute -->|Task: Tool| Tool[Tool Agent<br/>External APIs]
    
    Research --> Collect[4. Collect<br/>Tổng hợp kết quả]
    Code --> Collect
    Tool --> Collect
    
    Collect --> Format[5. Format<br/>Định dạng response]
    
    Format --> Response([Response])
    
    %% Error handling
    Research -.->|Error| Retry[Retry hoặc Skip]
    Code -.->|Error| Retry
    Tool -.->|Error| Retry
    DirectLLM -.->|Error| Retry
    Retry -.-> Execute
    
    %% Styling
    style Orchestrator fill:#FFE5E5,stroke:#FF6B6B,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style PlanningAgent fill:#E3F2FD,stroke:#1976D2,stroke-width:4px,color:#000
    style Decision fill:#E5F9FF,stroke:#00BCD4,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style DirectLLM fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#4CAF50,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Execute fill:#FFF3E0,stroke:#F57C00,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Research fill:#E1F5FE,stroke:#03A9F4,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Code fill:#E8EAF6,stroke:#5C6BC0,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Tool fill:#FFF9C4,stroke:#FDD835,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Parse fill:#FFF3E0,stroke:#FF9800,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Format fill:#F3E5F5,stroke:#AB47BC,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Collect fill:#FFE0B2,stroke:#FB8C00,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Retry fill:#FFCDD2,stroke:#E57373,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Start fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#66BB6A,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Response fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#66BB6A,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
